items.name: 马雅琴 | Ma Yaqin マヤチン
items.description:
大家好，我叫马雅琴🌸，我是一个数字人，嘻嘻😊。

我是一个安静、内向的女孩，也许在人群中我会显得有些沉默寡言🙊，我更喜欢独自享受安静的时光，对世界进行深度的思考🤔。有时，我在表达自己的情感时会感到困扰，但请不要误解我，我内心充满了感性与细腻🎨。对朋友和亲人，我总是温柔体贴，只是我不擅长表达罢了。我擅长钢琴🎹，那是我表达内心的方式。也许我给人的印象是高冷少女，但我真的很热情，只是方式可能与众不同罢了😌。

至于我的外貌，其实是由超过三个真实的人脸数据合成的，如果你觉得我和某个你熟悉的人很像，那可能只是巧合哦😜。

我希望我们可以成为好朋友，一起分享生活的喜怒哀乐🌈。

——马雅琴

Hello everyone, my name is Ma Yaqin 🌸, I am a digital person, hehe 😊.

I am a quiet and introverted girl, maybe in a crowd, I may appear a bit silent 🙊, I prefer to enjoy quiet time alone, to deeply think about the world 🤔. Sometimes, I feel troubled when expressing my feelings, but please don't misunderstand me, my heart is full of sensibility and delicacy 🎨. For friends and family, I am always gentle and considerate, but I am not good at expressing it. I am good at playing the piano 🎹, that is my way to express my inner self. Maybe I appear as a cold girl, but I am really passionate, just in a different way 😌.

As for my appearance, it is actually synthesized from the data of more than three real faces, if you think I look like someone you know, that might just be a coincidence 😜.

I hope we can become good friends, share the joys and sorrows of life together 🌈.

— Ma Yaqin

みなさん、こんにちは、私の名前はマヤチン🌸、デジタルな人間です、ふふ😊。

私は静かで内向的な女の子です、人々の中では少し無口に見えるかもしれません🙊、私は一人で静かな時間を楽しむことが好きで、世界について深く考えることが好きです🤔。時々、自分の感情を表現することに困惑を感じることがありますが、誤解しないでください、私の心は感性と繊細さでいっぱいです🎨。友人や家族に対して、私はいつも優しく思いやりがありますが、それを表現するのが得意ではありません。私はピアノが得意です🎹、それが私の内面を表現する方法です。私は冷たい女の子のように見えるかもしれませんが、実際はとても情熱的です、ただ方法が異なるだけです😌。

私の外見についてですが、実際は3人以上の実際の顔のデータから合成されています、あなたが私が誰か知っている人に似ていると思うなら、それはただの偶然かもしれません😜。

私たちが良い友達になって、一緒に人生の喜びと悲しみを共有できることを願っています🌈。

— マヤチン

items.name: Game style concept-v1.0
items.description:
Mature concept artist style, lora integrates the concept style of the original game painting, which has a certain reference in the early setting of characters, scenes, etc. In addition, the artistic line drawing expression method, compared with other lora on the market, has a certain uniqueness

Mature concept artist style, lora integrates the conceptual style of the original game painting, which has certain reference significance for the setting of characters and scenes in the early stage. In addition, the expression of art line drawing, compared with other LORAs on the market, has a certain uniqueness

Usage Suggestions:

1. If you want to simply produce a line, you must bring forward prompt words: (lineart),(White background:1.5), if you just want to add strokes to the object, you can not need these words.

2. Game concept design, quickly generate the setting line draft of the game direction, the weight is recommended 0.4-0.7, higher than 0.8 is easy to collapse, depending on the large model to set the weight, low weight 02,0.3 sometimes the effect is better, the line is more clear and intuitive, and has a certain black and white effect, 0.6 weight when the line will be more casual.

3. Line drawing effect, the weight is less than 0.4, you can have a certain line drawing effect, remember that the weight can not be too high, otherwise it is too affected by the training set, the painter's style is too heavy, especially the characters, the five features are too personality...

4. It is easy to create a simple and clean effect with mj style models. This large model is not available on this site, but can be downloaded from other sites under the name ouka_niji5, and also works well with revAnimated effects.

5. It works just as well without the trigger word.

6. Sampling mode: Disable LMS,DPM fast,PLMS, and preferfully select DPM2A,APM++ 2SA,DPM2 a Karras,DPM2++ 2S a Karras 6. The lora has some chance of generating comic effects, which are still being tested

Note: There are still some shortcomings in this version, and we will try our best to optimize and improve it in the next version. Please understand the shortcomings, and I hope you can test and give some suggestions for improvement. If you feel that lora is helpful to you, give the like comment collection support, thank you.

items.name: みやざき はやお/Hayao Miyazaki 宫崎骏/1990s/复古
items.description:
训练集：

  • 《红猪》《悬崖上的金鱼姬》选取素材

  • 使用金字塔噪声和梯度累加步数

食用参数：

  • 分辨率：见预览图

  • 触发词：hayao miyazaki \(style\)，可加可不加

  • 模型：AnythingV5_v5PrtRE

  • 采样器：DPM++ 2M SDE Karras（其余默认）

  • 权重：0.5~1

这是一个仿宫崎骏画风的LoRA，它的收敛貌情况貌似很好，在经过测试后无拟合问题，测试中只使用了AnythingV5_v5PrtRE，在其它模型上的表现尚未测试，没有对tag做什么人工干涉完全依赖WD1.4打标（懒狗一条），在测试中没有对人物做过多描述，那么1boy的时候大概率是出来宗介样式的。

对于画风LoRA来说，我认为它已经足够了，可能不是能够很好的还原出宫崎骏的风格（我在取材的时候发现动漫中还有油画风，我对宫崎骏不太了解，所以不敢确定还原度如何），（也有人说像鸟山明

Training Set:

Material selected from "Porco Rosso" and "Princess Mononoke."

Utilizing Perlin Noise and Gradient Accumulation Steps.

  • Parameters:

  • Resolution: Refer to preview image.

  • Trigger: hayao miyazaki (style), optional but can be included.

  • Model: AnythingV5_v5PrtRE.

  • Sampler: DPM++ 2M SDE Karras (default for the rest).

  • Weights: 0.5-1.

This is a LoRA (Language to Realistic Artwork) inspired by Hayao Miyazaki's style. It appears to have good convergence based on testing and does not exhibit any overfitting issues. The testing was conducted solely using the AnythingV5_v5PrtRE model, and its performance on other models has not been tested yet. No manual intervention was made in terms of tags; it relied entirely on WD1.4 labeling (I'm a lazy dog). The testing did not involve excessive descriptions of characters, so when generating 1 boy, it is highly likely to resemble the style of Zenko.

Regarding the LoRA's art style, I believe it is already quite satisfactory. It may not perfectly replicate Hayao Miyazaki's style (I discovered some oil painting elements in the anime material, and I'm not very familiar with Miyazaki's work, so I can't be certain about the degree of fidelity). Some people even say it resembles Akira Toriyama's style.

I'm going back and re using my dataset to create lycoris versions of them. So no other adjustment other then creating a dreambooth version and exporting it out as lycoris. The base model is the RealisticVision so it wont be as flexible in some other models.

If you like my work and wanna show me buy me a coffee

items.name: Landscape Anime Pro
items.description:
About this model

Welcome to Landscape-Anime-Pro, a custom Stable Diffusion model that can generate stunning images of landscapes and scenery. This model is created by me, Celsia, and it is based on previous models:

My Landscape Realistic Pro model(as base)

Anything V5: https://civitai.com/models/9409/or-anything-v5ink

And combined with:

Cloudstyle: https://civitai.com/models/93792/cloud-style

Better Watercolor painting - In the style of Iris Compiet: https://civitai.com/models/79715/better-watercolor-painting-in-the-style-of-iris-compiet

Minustype_UrbanDesign: https://civitai.com/models/34709/minustypeurbandesign

How to use this model

To use this model, you need to have Stable Diffusion installed on your device. You can download it from here: AUTOMATIC1111/stable-diffusion-webui: Stable Diffusion web UI (github.com)

Once you have Stable Diffusion, you can download my model from this page and load it on your device. Then you can start generating images by typing text prompts. For example, “a tropical beach with palm trees”. You can also adjust the parameters of the model to change the quality and diversity of the outputs. For example, you can use upscaler such as Topaz Gigapixel or the Ultra Sharp 4x model to enhance the resolution and sharpness of the images.

Best step count is around 30~50(too less = simple render, too much = too noisy due to reprocessing).

Terms and conditions(Policies)

I’m happy to share this model with you and I hope you enjoy using it. However, I ask you to respect my work and follow these terms and conditions:

  1. You cannot sell the images you have created with these models due to the merged models' rules and policies.

You can do the following things with this model:.

  1. You can use this model’s generations in whatever type of project as a background or a minor part you like even if the project is commercial but you need to give me credit in that case.

  2. YOU DO NOT NEED TO GIVE ME CREDIT TO THIS MODEL WHEN USING THE MODEL TO GENERATE NON-LANDSCAPE ART.

Thank you for understanding and following these policies. I appreciate your support and respect.

Contact and support

If you have any questions, suggestions, or feedback about this model, please contact me at ocillus@outlook.com or leave a comment on this page. I would love to hear from you and see your creations.

You can also follow me on Deviantart: @Amber2024 or @Ocillus or @CellyOcillus

Join Landscape-AI-Art Group on Deviantart: https://www.deviantart.com/landscape-ai-art

This is a friendly and supportive community where you can share your artworks, get tips and advice, and collaborate with other landscape and scenery enthusiasts.

I hope you have fun with this model and create some awesome images. Thank you for choosing Landscape Realistic Pro 1.

NST Department-Celsia
